<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 09:12:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>监管官员称中国FDI流入量波动属正常</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/volatility-chinas-fdi-inflows-is-normal-regulatory-official-says-2024-03-26/</link><description>周二，一名中国监管官员试图淡化世界第二大经济体外国直接投资（FDI）下滑的影响，称随着当局努力吸引外国资金，波动是“正常的”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 09:08:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/volatility-chinas-fdi-inflows-is-normal-regulatory-official-says-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>首席执行官表示瑞银将在五到六年内将来自亚洲的资产提高到20%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-boost-asia-sourced-assets-20-five-six-years-ceo-says-2024-03-26/</link><description>瑞银集团首席执行官塞尔吉奥·埃尔莫蒂(Sergio Ermotti)周二表示，瑞银集团计划利用亚洲的增长机会，在五六年内将来自该地区客户的资产增加至20%。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 08:46:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/ubs-boost-asia-sourced-assets-20-five-six-years-ceo-says-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>官员称中国商飞宽体客机C929处于“详细设计阶段”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-wide-body-c929-jet-detailed-design-stage-official-says-2024-03-26/</link><description>中国国有飞机制造商中国商飞的首架宽体飞机正处于“详细设计阶段”，一位高管周二表示，此前该飞机的机身制造商发布了一份计划于 2027 年 9 月交付首个机身部分的报告。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 08:39:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/chinas-comac-wide-body-c929-jet-detailed-design-stage-official-says-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>APT31：全球网络间谍活动背后的中国黑客组织</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/apt31-chinese-hacking-group-behind-global-cyberespionage-campaign-2024-03-26/</link><description>美国和英国对一家与中国国家支持的名为 APT31 的黑客组织有关联的公司和个人提出指控并实施制裁，称该组织参与了大规模的网络间谍活动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 08:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/apt31-chinese-hacking-group-behind-global-cyberespionage-campaign-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>韩国对中国对菲律宾船只使用高压水枪表示“严重关切”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-has-grave-concerns-over-china-using-water-cannons-against-philippine-2024-03-26/</link><description>韩国外交部周二对中国最近对菲律宾船只使用水炮表示“严重关切”，称这加剧了南海紧张局势并破坏了海上秩序。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 07:55:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/south-korea-has-grave-concerns-over-china-using-water-cannons-against-philippine-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国称美英黑客指控是“政治操纵”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/evidence-britain-provided-hacking-allegations-was-insufficient-says-chinese-2024-03-26/</link><description>中方敦促美英停止将网络安全问题政治化，停止污蔑抹黑中国，停止对中国实施单边制裁。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 07:54:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/evidence-britain-provided-hacking-allegations-was-insufficient-says-chinese-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>金砖国家开发银行计划2024年贷款50亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/brics-development-bank-aims-make-5-bln-loans-2024-2024-03-26/</link><description>由新兴经济体金砖国家集团设立的金砖国家新开发银行(NDB)副行长周强武周二表示，今年的目标是发放约50亿美元的贷款。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 06:13:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/brics-development-bank-aims-make-5-bln-loans-2024-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>官员称，武装分子袭击巴基斯坦海军基地造成六人死亡</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/six-killed-militant-attack-pakistan-naval-base-say-officials-2024-03-26/</link><description>官员周二表示，武装分子袭击了巴基斯坦海军空军基地，造成至少一名准军事士兵死亡，安全部队在报复性开火中击毙了所有五名袭击者。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 05:47:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/six-killed-militant-attack-pakistan-naval-base-say-officials-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国为应对低出生率和高成本，鼓励节俭婚礼</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-battling-low-birth-rates-high-costs-encourages-frugal-weddings-2024-03-26/</link><description>在负责妇女权利的政府机构发表了一篇敦促婚礼更加节俭的文章后，中国的年轻夫妇计划举办“简单”的婚礼，而不是传统的数百名宾客的宴会，成为网上最热门的话题之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 05:43:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-battling-low-birth-rates-high-costs-encourages-frugal-weddings-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，中国国家主席习近平将于周三会见美国高管</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-xi-jinping-meet-with-american-executives-wednesday-sources-say-2024-03-26/</link><description>据三位知情人士透露，中国国家主席习近平将于周三在北京会见美国商界领袖，这是他 11 月份在旧金山与美国投资者共进晚餐的后续行动。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 04:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-xi-jinping-meet-with-american-executives-wednesday-sources-say-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>合众集团推出新的 120 亿美元私募股权二级基金</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/partners-group-launches-new-12-bln-private-equity-secondaries-fund-2024-03-26/</link><description>瑞士投资公司 Partners Group 亚洲区主席周二表示，该公司已推出另一只价值高达 120 亿美元的私募股权二级策略基金，押注于二级市场交易量的增长。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 04:14:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/partners-group-launches-new-12-bln-private-equity-secondaries-fund-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行首席执行官温特斯会见中国外汇监管机构并成立投资银行部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-ceo-winters-meets-china-fx-regulator-launches-investment-banking-unit-2024-03-26/</link><description>渣打银行首席执行官比尔·温特斯(Bill Winters)周一会见了中国外汇监管机构负责人，一个月前，渣打银行暂停了中国客户通过配额渠道对离岸产品的新投资。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 03:33:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-ceo-winters-meets-china-fx-regulator-launches-investment-banking-unit-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>前中国足协主席因腐败被判无期徒刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/ex-head-china-football-association-sentenced-life-prison-state-media-report-2024-03-26/</link><description>据官方媒体周二报道，中国足协一名前主席因收受超过 1000 万美元的贿赂而被判处无期徒刑，此前这是足坛多年来最大规模的反腐败调查之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 02:30:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/ex-head-china-football-association-sentenced-life-prison-state-media-report-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国国务院表示，美国和越南高级外交官讨论加强芯片合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-vietnamese-top-diplomats-discuss-greater-chip-cooperation-state-dept-says-2024-03-26/</link><description>美国国务院表示，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯和越南外交部长裴青山周一在华盛顿举行的会议上讨论了扩大半导体和供应链多元化合作的问题。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 01:30:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-vietnamese-top-diplomats-discuss-greater-chip-cooperation-state-dept-says-2024-03-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾在清晨导弹演习中测试防空系统</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-tests-air-defences-early-morning-missile-drills-2024-03-26/</link><description>台湾在周二清晨的演习中使用地对空导弹以及空中、陆地和海军力量测试了其防空能力，并表示面对中国在附近频繁的军事活动，台湾将继续加强训练。</description><pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 00:41:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-tests-air-defences-early-morning-missile-drills-2024-03-26/</guid></item></channel></rss>